OL,3,GUK weather for today and tomorrow
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FLargely dry across the UK today
OL,6,Fwith prolonged sunny spells at first.
OL,7,FCloud will increase a little into the
OL,8,Fafternoon, particularly in the west.
OL,9,FScattered showers will also move into
OL,10,FNorthern Ireland and western Scotland.
OL,11,FWarm in the sunshine.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTonight:FA heavy spell of rain will
OL,14,Fmove into the northwest with brisk
OL,15,Fwinds. Drier elsewhere with clear
OL,16,Fspells and a fresh night for many.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
